                    "type": "software",
                    "rawForm": "CL",
                    "resp": "whitelist",
                    "id": "software-simple-w6"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "Figure 5: The observed 90% CL exclusion limits (red line) on the axion-electron coupling (g ae ) for the first 59.5 days data of COSINE-100 are shown together with the 68% and 95% probability bands for the expected 90% CL limit assuming the backgroundonly hypothesis. ",
            "section": "COSINE-100 setup and data",
            "paragraph_rank": 23,
            "section_rank": 5,
            "ref_spans": [
                {
                    "start": 0,
