                    "rawForm": "CL",
                    "resp": "whitelist",
                    "id": "software-simple-w8"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "The limits are compared with the results set by XMASS [31], EDELWEISS-III [32], KIMS [33], XENON100 [34], PandaX-II [35], and LUX [36] experiments together with indirect astrophysical bounds of solar neutrino [37].",
            "section": "COSINE-100 setup and data",
            "paragraph_rank": 23,
            "section_rank": 5,
            "ref_spans": [
